Not sure if it was really the best first impression, but I remember dan being absolutely hilarious in this video. ( I saw this after the rebrand, so when I googled “danisnotonfire” and “Daniel Howell” came up I was very confused)

However this was just the start … of a fast spiral into obsession .

Yes all 401 of those liked videos are DnP content
